
	Chilton Investment Company - Home Page


































A TIMELESS APPROACH TO HEDGE FUND INVESTING
Chilton Investment Company, LLC is a global investment management firm that aims to produce superior investment returns by aggressively seeking capital appreciation in rising markets and preserving capital in declining markets. We take a long-term perspective as we endeavor to maintain a focused, disciplined portfolio that consistently generates profits for our clients over time.


 







